data.description: Nestled in The Trails at Aspen Ridge, is a Better Than New two-story haven, a true upgrade in lifestyle. Majestic mountain views welcome you as you approach the manicured landscaping and perfectly sets the tone for what awaits inside. The moment you cross the threshold, a sense of grandeur  and sophistication envelops you. The open-concept great room, with tall ceilings and natural light, seamlessly connects to the kitchen and dining area for ultimate entertaining.  The bright and open kitchen features 42-inch white shaker cabinets, quartz countertops, stainless steel appliances and a spacious pantry for all your chef's tools. Retreat to the private backyard and patio to soak in the scenery of a nearby reservoir and endless mountain views.    Before venturing upstairs, beautiful French doors reveal to a luxurious main-level office. On the upper level, a built-in desk offers a great study area and is adjacent to a spacious laundry room. Three generously sized & thoughtfully situated secondary bedrooms offer privacy and togetherness with an adjoining loft. Each one a retreat in their own right  with ample space, large closets, and a stunning shared guest bath. The  primary bedroom is extravagant & provides a luxury 5-piece en-suite and dreamy walk-in closet.    The basement is a fully finished masterpiece, with an additional bedroom and gorgeous full bathroom offering flexibility for guests or a growing family. Storage is abundant throughout, ensuring that every belonging has its place. Make this space a haven of possibilities, from a cozy retreat to a vibrant entertainment space or home gym.  Experience the epitome of modern living in The Trails community in this home. With its centralized location, commuting to Schriever, Peterson, and Carson military bases has never been easier as it offers both convenience and tranquility in one perfect package.  Welcome home to a life of comfort, convenience, and timeless elegance.
